&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;As the EU GRC Manager, you will spearhead the implementation of security frameworks that align with DORA and MiCA, act as the primary liaison with our European customers on compliance matters, and collaborate with cross-functional teams to embed regulatory compliance into our operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Reporting line: GRC Director&lt;/p&gt;
